obviously, of being abandoned

00:02:35.240 --> 00:02:36.470
and that sort of thing.

00:02:36.470 --> 00:02:40.640
The latest research that
we have available to us

00:02:40.640 --> 00:02:44.060
shows that the only
way to conquer fear

00:02:44.060 --> 00:02:46.530
is to find more of it.

00:02:46.530 --> 00:02:48.330
Most people don't realize that.

00:02:48.330 --> 00:02:53.440
That to really tame fear,
you have to find more of it.

00:02:53.440 --> 00:02:55.980
So there's only two
choices you have.

00:02:55.980 --> 00:03:00.420
You can either tame fear,
or fear can tame you.

00:03:00.420 --> 00:03:02.850
There's no in-between.

00:03:02.850 --> 00:03:04.740
Ripping the lid off
those hidden fears

00:03:04.740 --> 00:03:06.367
will dramatically
change your life.

00:03:06.367 --> 00:03:07.950
They're going to
change your emotions.

00:03:07.950 --> 00:03:10.325
They'll change how you deal
with your colleagues at work,

00:03:10.325 --> 00:03:12.750
they'll change how you deal
with your friends and family,

00:03:12.750 --> 00:03:15.190
and they'll change how
you feel about yourself.

00:03:15.190 --> 00:03:18.060
